# README

* Ruby version : 2.5.3
* Require a working postgres instance (use docker-compose)

# Setup

* `docker-compose up -d`
* `rails db:setup`
* `rails db:migrate`
* `rails s`
* Navigate to `localhost:3000`

# Api

Api Doc is available here : https://aurelienblais.github.io/ihm-back/apidoc.html
